criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  18 years of age of older;

          -  Meet the diagnostic criteria for dry eye developed by DEWS II: OSDI score≥15 points,
             TBUT≤10 minutes;

          -  Meet the signs of meibomian gland dysfunction

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Had skin allergies or inflammation;

          -  Had active ocular infection or inflammation;

          -  Had history of ocular surgery, eyelid surgery or neurological paralysis within 6
             months;

          -  Had history of systemic disease affecting ocular surface function, such as
             Stevens-Johnson syndrome, Sjögren syndrome etc.
